{
  "page": "Black council",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center;\">Black council</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/250px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/375px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/500px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a></div></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; margin-bottom:10px;\">The sigil of <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Type</th><td>\nCouncil</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Seat</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a> <small>(briefly)</small></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founder</th><td>\nRhaenyra Targaryen</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founded</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/129_AC\" title=\"129 AC\">129&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Disbanded</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>black council</b> was a version of the <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a> which advised <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>. Formed at the start of the civil war, the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">black</a> council's main composition was:<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\"><img alt=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/20px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/30px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/40px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\"><img alt=\"House Velaryon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/20px-House_Velaryon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/30px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/40px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Corlys_Velaryon\" title=\"Corlys Velaryon\">Corlys Velaryon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenys_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aemon)\" title=\"Rhaenys Targaryen (daughter of Aemon)\">Rhaenys Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\"><img alt=\"House Velaryon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/20px-House_Velaryon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/30px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/40px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Jacaerys_Velaryon\" title=\"Jacaerys Velaryon\">Jacaerys Velaryon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\"><img alt=\"House Velaryon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/20px-House_Velaryon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/30px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/40px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Lucerys_Velaryon\" title=\"Lucerys Velaryon\">Lucerys Velaryon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\"><img alt=\"House Velaryon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/20px-House_Velaryon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/30px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/40px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Velaryon\" title=\"Joffrey Velaryon\">Joffrey Velaryon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/20px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/30px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/40px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Erryk_Cargyll\" title=\"Erryk Cargyll\">Erryk Cargyll</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/20px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/30px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/40px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lorent_Marbrand\" title=\"Lorent Marbrand\">Lorent Marbrand</a></li></ul>\n<p>There were also a dozen lesser lords, bannermen and vassals of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>, including:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Celtigar\" title=\"House Celtigar\"><img alt=\"House Celtigar 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_Celtigar_2.svg/20px-House_Celtigar_2.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_Celtigar_2.svg/30px-House_Celtigar_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/House_Celtigar_2.svg/40px-House_Celtigar_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Bartimos_Celtigar\" title=\"Bartimos Celtigar\">Bartimos Celtigar</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Claw_Isle\" title=\"Claw Isle\">Claw Isle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Staunton\" title=\"House Staunton\"><img alt=\"House Staunton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/20px-House_Staunton.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/30px-House_Staunton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/House_Staunton.svg/40px-House_Staunton.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Staunton\" title=\"Lord Staunton\">Staunton</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Rook%27s_Rest\" title=\"Rook&#39;s Rest\">Rook's Rest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Massey\" title=\"House Massey\"><img alt=\"House Massey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/20px-House_Massey.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/30px-House_Massey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/06/House_Massey.svg/40px-House_Massey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gormon_Massey\" title=\"Gormon Massey\">Gormon Massey</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonedance\" title=\"Stonedance\">Stonedance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"House Bar Emmon\"><img alt=\"House Bar Emmon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/20px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/30px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/40px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"House Bar Emmon\">Bar Emmon</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Sharp_Point\" title=\"Sharp Point\">Sharp Point</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Darklyn\" title=\"House Darklyn\"><img alt=\"House Darklyn.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Darklyn.svg/20px-House_Darklyn.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Darklyn.svg/30px-House_Darklyn.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/House_Darklyn.svg/40px-House_Darklyn.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Darklyn\" title=\"Gunthor Darklyn\">Gunthor Darklyn</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a></li></ul>\n<p>After the <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Fall of King&#39;s Landing\">Fall of King's Landing</a>, Rhaenyra took the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> and named several members to her <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a>.\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\"><img alt=\"House Velaryon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/20px-House_Velaryon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/30px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/House_Velaryon.svg/40px-House_Velaryon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Corlys_Velaryon\" title=\"Corlys Velaryon\">Corlys Velaryon</a> was named the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the Queen</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\"><img alt=\"Maester.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/20px-Maester.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/30px-Maester.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/Maester.svg/40px-Maester.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Gerardys\" title=\"Gerardys\">Gerardys</a> was named her <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Celtigar\" title=\"House Celtigar\"><img alt=\"House Celtigar 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_Celtigar_2.svg/20px-House_Celtigar_2.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/09/House_Celtigar_2.svg/30px-House_Celtigar_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/09/House_Celtigar_2.svg/40px-House_Celtigar_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Bartimos_Celtigar\" title=\"Bartimos Celtigar\">Bartimos Celtigar</a> was named <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_coin\" title=\"Master of coin\">master of coin</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing\"><img alt=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/20px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/30px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/75/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg/40px-City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Luthor_Largent\" title=\"Luthor Largent\">Luthor Largent</a>, the Commander of the City Watch.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\"><img alt=\"Kingsguard.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/20px-Kingsguard.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/30px-Kingsguard.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6d/Kingsguard.svg/40px-Kingsguard.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lorent_Marbrand\" title=\"Lorent Marbrand\">Lorent Marbrand</a>, the Lord Commander of the Queensguard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\"><img alt=\"House Manderly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/20px-House_Manderly.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/30px-House_Manderly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/40px-House_Manderly.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Medrick_Manderly\" title=\"Medrick Manderly\">Medrick Manderly</a>, the heir to <a href=\"/index.php/White_Harbor\" title=\"White Harbor\">White Harbor</a>, an advisor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\"><img alt=\"House Manderly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/20px-House_Manderly.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/30px-House_Manderly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/40px-House_Manderly.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Manderly\" title=\"Torrhen Manderly\">Torrhen Manderly</a>, younger brother to Medrick, an advisor.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/20px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/30px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/40px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Mysaria\" title=\"Mysaria\">Mysaria</a>, an advisor and unofficially the <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_whisperers\" title=\"Master of whisperers\">mistress of whisperers</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_council&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>And so <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">the dance began</a>, as the princess called a council of her own. \"The <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">black</a> council\", setting it against the \"<a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">green council</a>\" of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Black_council&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - The Blacks and the Greens.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtrotd81.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\">2.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i>, The Reign of Aegon II&#58; The Dance of the Dragons.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>